---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTA from '../components/CTA.astro';
import { business } from '../data/business';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us | Healthy Paws Animal Hospital"
  description="Learn about Healthy Paws Animal Hospital in Lake in the Hills, IL — founded in 2010 by Dr. Burgess. A privately owned, women-owned practice dedicated to gentle, low-stress care, built on transparency, education, and personal care."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-hpah-green-light py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="text-hpah-green font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">About Our Practice</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl mb-6">The Practice We Always Wished Existed</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-hpah-text-light">
        Healthy Paws Animal Hospital was born from a simple idea: veterinary medicine should be personal,
        transparent, and built around education — not corporate efficiency metrics. Since 2010, that idea
        has guided everything we do.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-3">
          <h2 class="mb-6">Our Story</h2>
          <p>
            In May 2010, Dr. Burgess opened the doors to Healthy Paws Animal Hospital in Lake in the Hills, Illinois,
            with a clear vision: build the veterinary practice she always wished existed. After graduating from
            Kansas State University College of Veterinary Medicine in 1997 and spending over a decade practicing
            veterinary medicine, she had seen firsthand what worked — and what didn't — in the way animals
            and their families were cared for.
          </p>
          <p>
            Too often, she saw practices that rushed through appointments, left pet owners confused about
            their options, and treated animals as cases rather than family members. She knew there was a
            better way. So she built it.
          </p>
          <p>
            From day one, Healthy Paws was designed around three principles: <strong>transparency</strong> in
            every interaction, <strong>education</strong> at every appointment, and <strong>personal care</strong>
            that treats every pet and owner as individuals. These aren't marketing slogans — they're the
            foundation of how we practice medicine every single day.
          </p>
          <p>
            What started as a single veterinarian with a vision has grown into a dedicated team of three
            doctors and a compassionate support staff. But the core hasn't changed. We're still privately owned,
            still women-owned, and still committed to the kind of care that made Dr. Burgess build this
            practice in the first place.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <div class="bg-hpah-green-light rounded-lg p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl mb-4 text-hpah-green">Quick Facts</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-hpah-text-light">
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="font-bold text-hpah-text">Founded:</span> May 2010
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="font-bold text-hpah-text">Owner:</span> Dr. Burgess, DVM
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="font-bold text-hpah-text">Location:</span> {business.address.city}, {business.address.state}
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="font-bold text-hpah-text">Approach:</span> Gentle, Low-Stress Care
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="font-bold text-hpah-text">Ownership:</span> Privately &amp; Women-Owned
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="font-bold text-hpah-text">Tagline:</span> {business.tagline}
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Philosophy -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-hpah-bg-warm">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-hpah-text-light mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Three principles guide every decision we make, every recommendation we offer,
          and every interaction we have with you and your pet.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-gray-100 text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-hpah-green-light rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-hpah-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl mb-3">Transparency</h3>
          <p class="text-hpah-text-light">
            You deserve to know exactly what's happening with your pet's care and why. We explain every
            diagnosis, every treatment option, and every cost before we proceed. We discuss what we recommend,
            what the alternatives are, and what happens if you choose to wait. No surprises. No hidden fees.
            No pressure. Just honest, open communication so you can make the best decisions for your family.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-gray-100 text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-hpah-green-light rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-hpah-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl mb-3">Education</h3>
          <p class="text-hpah-text-light">
            We believe informed pet owners make the best decisions. That's why we take the time at every
            appointment to explain the "why" behind our recommendations — not just the "what." We want you
            to understand your pet's health, recognize early warning signs at home, and feel confident in
            the care plan we build together. When you leave our office, you should feel empowered, not confused.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-gray-100 text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-hpah-green-light rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-hpah-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl mb-3">Personal Care</h3>
          <p class="text-hpah-text-light">
            Your pet isn't a number on a chart. We remember names, we know histories, and we care about
            the little details that make your pet unique. From personal follow-up calls after surgery
            to remembering that your cat prefers a specific exam room, we treat every family the way we'd
            want our own pets treated. That's the advantage of a privately owned practice — we have the
            freedom to prioritize relationships over volume.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Makes Us Different -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-hpah-text-light mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          We didn't just adopt a philosophy — we designed our entire practice around it. From the physical
          layout of our hospital to the technology we use, every detail serves a purpose.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-hpah-green-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <span class="text-xl">💚</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl mb-2">Gentle, Low-Stress Care</h3>
            <p class="text-hpah-text-light">
              Our entire team — doctors and staff alike — is trained in gentle handling techniques that reduce
              fear, anxiety, and stress during every veterinary visit. We use gentle handling, calming
              environments, and patient-centered protocols so your pet's emotional well-being is treated
              with the same importance as their physical health.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-hpah-green-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <span class="text-xl">🚪</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl mb-2">Single Exam Room Design</h3>
            <p class="text-hpah-text-light">
              When you arrive at Healthy Paws, your pet goes directly to the exam room — not to a crowded
              lobby full of other anxious animals. Our lobby is small by design because we consider it a
              failure if you spend significant time there. This approach reduces stress for your pet and
              ensures your visit begins the moment you walk through the door.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-hpah-green-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <span class="text-xl">🔬</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl mb-2">Comprehensive In-House Laboratory</h3>
            <p class="text-hpah-text-light">
              Our in-house laboratory allows us to run blood work, urinalysis, and other critical diagnostics
              right here in our hospital. That means faster results, faster diagnoses, and faster treatment
              for your pet. You won't have to wait days wondering what's wrong — in most cases, we have
              answers during your visit.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-hpah-green-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <span class="text-xl">🧾</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl mb-2">In-Room Checkout</h3>
            <p class="text-hpah-text-light">
              Your visit ends where it began — in the exam room. We handle checkout right there, so you
              never have to stand at a front desk juggling a leash, a pet carrier, and a credit card.
              It's a small detail, but it's the kind of detail that makes a big difference in your experience.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Commitment -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-hpah-bg-warm">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-6">Our Commitment to You</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-hpah-text-light mb-6">
        When you bring your pet to Healthy Paws Animal Hospital, you're not just visiting a veterinary
        clinic — you're joining a community. We're committed to being your partner in your pet's health
        for every stage of their life, from their very first puppy or kitten visit through their senior
        years and beyond.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-hpah-text-light mb-6">
        We promise to always be honest with you, to always explain our reasoning, and to always
        respect your role as the most important advocate your pet has. We promise to stay privately owned,
        to keep making decisions based on medicine rather than corporate directives, and to keep
        investing in the training and technology that allows us to provide the best care possible.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-hpah-text-light">
        Most importantly, we promise to treat your pet the way we'd treat our own. Because at the end
        of the day, that's exactly why Dr. Burgess built this practice.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTA heading="Come See the Difference for Yourself" text="Schedule a visit and discover what veterinary care looks like when it's built around your pet — not a corporate model." />
</BaseLayout>
